    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with administrative controls in place. CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for worst-case hemolysis identification across the CPB operating envelope. RH < 1 acceptance criterion met at all five operating points with maximum CFD-to-experimental discrepancy of 11.3%, within the 15% acceptance band. Model credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
